column6: DIE HARD in the Sanctum Sanctorum! With Dr. Strange elsewhere, magical terrorists have taken over Strange's sanctum! Agent Coulson must lead a strike team into the mansion before time runs out for New York City, and his only available allies are Spider-Man and one of Strange's oldest foes!
column8: | artist:Alan Davis | penciller (cover):Julian Totino Tedesco | writer:Mark Waid
